OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FNewcastle have vowed to track down
OL,7,Fthose responsible for discriminatory
OL,8,Fabuse aimed at Sunderland defender
OL,9,FLutsharel Geertruida during Sunday's
OL,10,FTyne-Wear derby.
OL,12,FReferee Anthony Taylor briefly paused
OL,13,Fthe game and spoke to both managers
OL,14,Fand club officials during the second
OL,15,Fhalf of the Magpies' 2-1 Premier
OL,16,FLeague defeat by their neighbours at
OL,17,FSt James' Park after an incident had
OL,18,Fbeen reported to him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FNewcastle later said in a statement:
OL,7,F"We are aware of a report of racism
OL,8,Fmade by a visiting player against
OL,9,Fsomeone in the crowd during our
OL,10,FPremier League match against
OL,11,FSunderland.
OL,13,F"Our stance is clear ` we do not
OL,14,Ftolerate discrimination of any form.
OL,15,FWe will work with the authorities to
OL,16,Ffully investigate and will ensure any
OL,17,Findividuals are identified and held
OL,18,Faccountable."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FThe Premier League said it will
OL,7,Finvestigate the incident under its on-
OL,8,Ffield anti-discrimination protocol.
OL,10,FTaylor had been approached by
OL,11,FSunderland captain Granit Xhaka in the
OL,12,F52nd minute, when the game was already
OL,13,Fstopped due to an injury to
OL,14,FNewcastle's Sven Botman.
OL,16,FTaylor spoke to both sets of coaches,
OL,17,FXhaka and Geertruida before restarting
OL,18,Fthe game.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FA social media post from the Premier
OL,7,FLeague Match Centre read: "The
OL,8,Fincident at St James' Park will now be
OL,9,Ffully investigated. We offer our full
OL,10,Fsupport to the player and both clubs.
OL,12,F"Racism has no place in our game, or
OL,13,Fanywhere in society. We will continue
OL,14,Fto work with stakeholders and
OL,15,Fauthorities to ensure our stadiums are
OL,16,Fan inclusive and welcoming environment
OL,17,Ffor all."
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
