FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FNewcastle were leading 1-0 at the time
OL,7,Fof the incident through Anthony
OL,8,FGordon's early goal, but Sunderland
OL,9,Fcame back to win 2-1 with goals from
OL,10,FChemsdine Talbi and Brian Brobbey.
OL,12,FAsked if he had spoken to Geertruida,
OL,13,Fvictorious Black Cats coach Regis Le
OL,14,FBris said after the game: "We spoke
OL,15,Fjust a bit before the press
OL,16,Fconference. He looks OK.
OL,18,F"It's not acceptable and it's
OL,19,Fimportant to report and to manage the
OL,20,Fsituation properly. He looks okay, but
OL,21,Fwe need to support him."
OL,26,@vD@[OUzD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
