CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FOpposite number Eddie Howe said: "I
OL,7,Fdon't know too much about it. All I'd
OL,8,Fsay is we don't condone racism of any
OL,9,Fform and the club will investigate."
OL,11,FA Sunderland spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Sunderland AFC is aware of the
OL,13,Freported incident of racist abuse
OL,14,Fdirected at Lutsharel Geertruida
OL,15,Fduring today's fixture at St. James'
OL,16,FPark.
OL,26,@nD@bOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,F"We stand with Lutsharel, who has our
OL,7,Fcomplete backing, and we commend him
OL,8,Ffor displaying bravery and leadership
OL,9,Fby reporting this incident to the
OL,10,Fmatch officials.
OL,12,F"Racism is completely unacceptable. It
OL,13,Fis abhorrent, and has no place in our
OL,14,Fgame or in society.
OL,16,F"We acknowledge Newcastle United's
OL,17,Fstatement and expect those responsible
OL,18,Fto be identified and held accountable.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,F"There can be no tolerance, no
OL,7,Fexcuses, and no ambiguity when it
OL,8,Fcomes to incidents of this nature.
OL,10,F"Football must be a safe and inclusive
OL,11,Fenvironment for everyone - without
OL,12,Fexception - and we will continue to
OL,13,Fwork with the relevant authorities to
OL,14,Fsupport that aim."
OL,16,FShow Racism the Red Card, the anti-
OL,17,Fracism education organisation, posted
OL,18,Fon social media platform X that it
OL,19,Fwould be meeting with Newcastle United
OL,20,Fabout the incident on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
