CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774444274
OL,3,CNewcastle vow action after alleged
OL,4,Cracist abuse halts Tyne-Wear derby
OL,6,FSeparately, Northumbria Police said
OL,7,Fone arrest had been made before the
OL,8,Fmatch following reports of clashes
OL,9,Fbetween rival supporters.
OL,11,F"We are aware of a number of videos
OL,12,Fcirculating on social media in
OL,13,Frelation to Newcastle United and
OL,14,FSunderland supporters goading one
OL,15,Fanother," the police said.
OL,17,F"In the main, everyone has co-operated
OL,18,Fand we are able to report that one
OL,19,Farrest was made ahead of kick-off.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@IO]yD@AOU
